eneren Sprachen ermöglichen praktische Übungen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mrz 2021) 4aLinguistik. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aAustin, J. L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBehaghel, O., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBergenholtz, H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBierwisch, M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBühler, K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChomsky, N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDanes, F., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDik, S. C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEhlich, K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEisenberg, P., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrege, G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrosch, H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrice, H. P., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGünthner, S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeeschen, V., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHockett, Ch., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoffmann, L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoffmann, Ludger, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHumboldt, W. V., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacobs, J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJakobson, R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabu